you know I mean it was just a sound but we've turned it into a disturbing noise you see so if you if we can grasp the idea that when the Buddha's talking about liberation and karma he's talking really about the world we're creating inside ourselves that's the real karma that's the real comeuppance so when you do something harmful the karmic result of that is not being put in jail

